description:
This Cloudish Agent 64bit package will install and configure all the required files needed to collect performance data of your Windows Azure .Net Web and Worker roles. For more information please visit http://www.cloudish.net to get your FREE account and start monitoring now.

For detailed installation instructions please visit http://support.cloudish.net

To Install:

1. When prompted, enter your Company Name, Cloudish Api Key (You can get your FREE key at http://www.cloudish.net), and the name of your main EXE/DLL.
2. This package will set up your Web or Worker role to install the Cloudish Agent when your instances start up.
3. Simply publish your application to Azure and the Cloudish agent will start collecting performance data.

title: Cloudish Agent 64bit
